item.title: Winning the Entrepreneurial Race: The Power of a Spartan Mindset for Optimum Performance with Coach Reed Maltbie
item.description:
Coach Reed Maltbie has dedicated his life to creating the very best environments for achieving peak performance.

With over 30 years of professional coaching experience, he knows first hand the power of language to create optimal performance.

His new book, The Spartan Mindset, focuses significantly on the impact of language on performance... Feed: https://feeds.buzzsprout.com/1139753.rss
